@startuml
title Sequence 02 - Mencari Lowongan
autonumber
actor "Pengunjung/Mahasiswa" as User
participant "Frontend Web" as FE
participant "Vacancy API\n/api/v1/vacancies" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> FE: Buka landing/public lowongan
FE -> API: GET /vacancies?page&per_page
API -> DB: Query Vacancies is_active=true
DB --> API: Daftar lowongan publik
API --> FE: Paginated vacancies
FE --> User: Tampilkan daftar lowongan

User -> FE: Masukkan keyword/filter
FE -> API: GET /vacancies/search?q&filters
API -> DB: Search active vacancies + company + skills
DB --> API: Hasil pencarian
alt hasil ditemukan
  API --> FE: Daftar lowongan relevan
  FE --> User: Tampilkan hasil
else kosong
  API --> FE: Empty list
  FE --> User: Tampilkan state kosong
end
@enduml
